Create Water

This spell causes a small amount of water to pour out of
thin air, even in the most barren desert.  It will refill
a waterskin.  At higher levels of mastery, the druid will
also be able to conjure the waterskin itself.

Command: cwater
Base Cost: 10 SP
Base Recovery: short
Base Effect: create items (water)
Base Duration: permanent
Guild Level: 3
